\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $P(x)=\underbrace{f(y_{0})}_{f[y_{0}]N_{0}(x)}+\underbrace{f'(y_{0})(x-y_{0})}_{f[y_{0},y_{1}]N_{1}(x)}$
\end_inset


