\begin_inset Formula $\tilde{T_{k+1}^{i}(x)}=\frac{T_{k}^{i}(x)(y_{i+k+1}-x)-T_{k}^{i+1}(x)(y_{i}-x)}{y_{i+k+1}-y_{i}}$
\end_inset

 et prouvons que 
